chainId: chainId of network tx should be executed on
proxyAddress: substrate proxy address, leave as empty if not executed by proxy

extrinsics.palletName: on which pallet this extrinsic will be executed
extrinsics.hex-encodedCallData: hex encoded call data that used to decode the extrinsic details on polkadot js app
extrinsics.blockHash: hash of the block that extrinsic got finalized
extrinsics.extrinsicID: extrinsic identifier, for example: 5729508-2 where 5729508 is the block height, 2 is the extrinsic index in the block
